{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                                 // hydrogen // schema // geometry // symmetry"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Symmetry — Geometric symmetry primitives for design systems."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Design Philosophy"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Symmetry describes invariance under transformation. A shape has symmetry"},{"LineComment":" | when it looks the same after applying certain operations (reflection,"},{"LineComment":" | rotation, translation). This module provides:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Reflection symmetry**: Mirror across an axis (bilateral)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Rotational symmetry**: N-fold rotation about a center"},{"LineComment":" | - **Translational symmetry**: Periodic repetition"},{"LineComment":" | - **Compound symmetry**: Combinations (dihedral, wallpaper groups)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Use Cases"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - Layout systems (bilateral UI layouts)"},{"LineComment":" | - Icon/logo generation (radial, dihedral)"},{"LineComment":" | - Pattern/tile generation (wallpaper groups)"},{"LineComment":" | - Procedural geometry (snowflakes, mandalas)"},{"LineComment":" | - Accessibility (symmetric UI aids comprehension)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Mathematical Foundation"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Symmetries form groups under composition:"},{"LineComment":" | - Identity is always a symmetry"},{"LineComment":" | - Every symmetry has an inverse"},{"LineComment":" | - Composition of symmetries is a symmetry"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Module Structure"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This is a leader module that re-exports from:"},{"LineComment":" | - Symmetry.Reflection — Mirror axes"},{"LineComment":" | - Symmetry.Rotational — N-fold rotation"},{"LineComment":" | - Symmetry.Dihedral — Rotation + reflection"},{"LineComment":" | - Symmetry.Translational — Periodic repetition"},{"LineComment":" | - Symmetry.Glide — Reflection + translation"},{"LineComment":" | - Symmetry.Group — Combined symmetry types"},{"LineComment":" | - Symmetry.Operations — Symmetry transformations"},{"LineComment":" | - Symmetry.Chirality — Handedness"},{"LineComment":" | - Symmetry.PointGroup — 2D point groups"},{"LineComment":" | - Symmetry.Wallpaper — 17 crystallographic groups"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Dependencies"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - Prelude (Eq, Ord, Show)"},{"LineComment":" | - Geometry.Angle (rotation angles)"},{"LineComment":" | - Data.Maybe (optional values)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Dependents"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - Schema.Geometry.Shape (symmetric shape construction)"},{"LineComment":" | - Schema.Geometry.Transform (symmetry-based transforms)"},{"LineComment":" | - Component.ColorPicker (radial symmetry)"},{"LineComment":" | - Component.Icon (logo symmetries)"}],"decls":[],"exports":[],"foreign":[],"imports":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[183,4],"start":[178,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Symmetry","Chirality"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[138,4],"start":[127,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Symmetry","Dihedral"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[159,4],"start":[152,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Symmetry","Glide"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[176,4],"start":[161,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Symmetry","Group"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[195,4],"start":[185,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Symmetry","Operations"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[203,4],"start":[